**Background of the enterprise**

  The Butterfly Exchange Agency is an online company with searches for solutions for destinations and courses that meet the profile and budget corresponding to each of our clients. The company outsources the sale of English courses, accommodation for students and exams in several countries They have as mission:
                *“Make the exchange experience a personalized personal transformation process for each of our students”*
                
